Summing Two Numbers

Source: R/sum.R
sum_two_numbers.Rd

Summing Two Numbers

Usage

sum_two_numbers(number1, number2)

Arguments

number1

first summand.

number2

second summand.

Value

The sum of number1 and number2.

Examples

sum_two_numbers(4, 1)
#> [1] 5
